   'It is used for COMPCODE of STRNDTL and BRANCD of STFETRAN';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.DOCTTYPE IS
   'It is used for DOCTTYPE of STRNDTL and DOCTYP of STFETRAN';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.SUBTTYPE IS
   'It is used for SUBTTYPE of STRNDTL';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.DOCNUMBR IS
   'It is used for DOCNUMBR of STRNDTL and DOCNUM of STFETRAN';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.DOCTDATE IS
   'It is used for DOCTDATE of STRNDTL and DOCDAT of STFETRAN';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.SERLNUMB IS
   'It is used for SERLNUMB of STRNDTL and SERNUM of STFETRAN';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.NOSTCODE IS 'It is used for NOSTROCODE';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.NOSTDATE IS
   'It is used for NOSTROVALUE DATE';

COMMENT ON COLUMN STLBAS.STTRDETL.NOSTRFNO IS
   'It is used for store Head Office exchange rate ';

